OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775304668
OL,3,CUnion says more strikes at Greater
OL,4,CManchester hospitals in overtime row
OL,6,FStaff working in critical care units
OL,7,Fat Salford Royal Hospital, Royal
OL,8,FOldham Hospital and Fairfield Hospital
OL,9,Fin Bury are set to stage further
OL,10,Fwalkouts in a row over pay.
OL,12,FNurses, clinical support workers and
OL,13,Fhousekeepers are among the Northern
OL,14,FCare Alliance (NCA) employees who will
OL,15,Fwalk out for 24 hours on Tuesday 7
OL,16,FApril.
OL,18,FThe walk out is separate to the
OL,19,Fresident doctors strike in England
OL,20,Fwhich starts on Tuesday next week and
OL,21,Fis due to last six days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
