OL,3,CUnion says more strikes at Greater
OL,4,CManchester hospitals in overtime row
OL,6,FThe strikes will start at 7am at
OL,7,FSalford Royal Hospital and at 7.30am
OL,8,Fat Royal Oldham and Fairfield.
